Brief History
=============

Infinity was originally written by Julien Carme on 2000.
Then the project froze for a couple of years, from 2001 to 2004 I guess.
In 2003 I came across this plugin and found it really beautiful so I decided
to improve it by adding MMX support and creating a project in Sourceforge.
2009: Infinity moved to Audacious media player based on the old good XMMS.
2013: the project moved into Github.
2016: code went from 100% C to mix of C / C++ to match Audacious 3.6 API.
2026: Build switched from autotools to meson. C++17 ports and improvements.
